RequestChoice >ENV:alma Title "Start AB3DII-TKG" Body "This will starts the game after an automatic reboot!*NYour current jobs will be lost*NSelect PATCH to start TKG with Aki Laukkanen's turbo patch." Gadgets Start|Patch|Cancel
if $alma gt 0
C/Mount TKG0: from Devs/TKG-Mountlist
C/Makedir TKG0:C
C/Makedir TKG0:S
C/Copy C/Remrad TKG0:C/
C/Copy C/Reset TKG0:C/
C/Copy C/Assign TKG0:C/
C/Edit from AB3DII-TKG to TKG0:S/Startup-Assign with Bootfiles/Edit_makro
endif
if $alma eq 1
C/Join TKG0:S/Startup-Assign BootFiles/Startup-TKG To TKG0:S/Startup-sequence
C/Reset
endif
if $alma eq 2
C/Join TKG0:S/Startup-Assign BootFiles/Startup-Turbo To TKG0:S/Startup-sequence
C/Reset
endif

